This project looks at the alternatives to heat pumps and hydrogen for the rapid, scalable, inclusive approaches to getting people off gas.

I wrote [a blog on LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/heat-pumps-arent-silver-bullet-adam-cooper/?trackingId=z3CDKR1mlMJ4DUbxVTnbaw%3D%3D) about my own personal reflections on the issues facing homeowners in smaller properties. 

